Jesse Tyler Ferguson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jesse_Tyler_Ferguson 0 Jesse Tyler Ferguson (born October 22, 1975) is an American actor. He is best known for portraying Mitchell Pritchett on the famous comedy series Modern Family (2009–present), which earned him five consecutive Primetime Emmy Award nominations.
